enb_long_title: Eleventh session of the Conference of the Parties to the Climate Change Convention and first meeting of the Parties to the Kyoto Protocol
sentences: Informal consultations continued on future commitments under Protocol Article 3.9.
Delegates agreed not to discuss Article 9 (review of the Protocol) in this group until Article 3.9 is dealt with.
The discussion then focused on whether to proceed with an ad hoc open-ended working group or workshops.
